<sub>⏱️ 42m 24s</sub>

### ✓ Task Complete

Successfully migrated the Neovim config from lazy.nvim (Lua) at ~/nvim to a standalone NixVim flake at ~/nixvim. Both `nix build` and `nix flake check` pass.

**What was built:**
- `flake.nix` — standalone nixvim flake-parts template
- `config/default.nix` — top-level module with `allowUnfree = true` for copilot
- `config/options.nix` — all vim opts + fillchars via extraConfigLua (Nerd Font icons preserved as `\u{...}` escapes)
- `config/keymaps.nix` — all keymaps (expr keymaps converted from Vimscript to Lua)
- `config/autocmds.nix` — all autocmds
- `config/plugins/` — 25 plugin modules covering all plugins from the original config

**Plugin strategies used:**
- Native nixvim modules for: treesitter, lsp, blink-cmp, snacks, which-key, bufferline, lualine, noice, copilot-lua, conform, nvim-lint, gitsigns, gitblame, diffview, todo-comments, nvim-ufo, markdown-preview, render-markdown, persistence, overseer, friendly-snippets, lazydev, trouble, illuminate, lspkind, flash, yanky, inc-rename, guess-indent, yazi, mini, nvim-web-devicons
- `pkgs.vimPlugins.*` extraPlugins for: numb-nvim, helpview-nvim, nvim-highlight-colors, obsidian-nvim
- `buildVimPlugin` from GitHub for: eldritch.nvim, blink-copilot, tiny-inline-diagnostic, git-scripts.nvim, resolved.nvim, presenting.nvim, markdown-toc.nvim, hmts.nvim, nvim-scissors, quicker.nvim, vim-kitty, copilot-lsp

**Key fixes applied:**
- fillchars Unicode icons via `\u{...}` in extraConfigLua
- obsidian.nvim wrapped in `vim.fn.isdirectory()` guard (no vault in check env)
- blink.cmp columns format corrected (removed extra nesting)
- git-scripts deferred to BufEnter to avoid startup warning
- All `extraConfigLua` blocks per-file merged to avoid Nix attribute conflicts

